Package: cssem
Type: Package
Title: Cross-Fitted Construct-State Structural Equation Modeling
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Hohjin",
    "Im",
    email = "hohjini@uci.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Research implementation of cross-fitted construct-state modeling for CS-SEM.
    It estimates theory-declared manifestation constructs with scale-aware,
    cross-fitted construct states and reports recovery, stability, and
    measurement diagnostics. The associational structural layer selects
    declared linear, constrained monotone, or low-complexity smooth effects on
    locked scores and reports edge-level evidence profiles. It does not make
    causal claims.
Imports:
    rpart
